original: Don't Touch What You Can't Afford

Ladies! Put some order in your eating disorder with the most over-the-top, in-your-face designer jeans you have ever seen! $400 in the stores, $80 on Designer Slave! They give any girl above size zero instant camel toe!
translated: 女士们！用你所见过的最夸张、最刺激的名牌牛仔裤，给自己的厌食症加点料吧！XXS码以上的姑娘瞬间就能得到骆驼趾！
